---
import "./Approach.css";
---

<section class="approach-section">
    <div class="top-banner">
        <ul>
            <li>
                AS A TOP-RATED KITCHEN REMODELING COMPANY IN MARYLAND, OUR TEAM KNOWS THAT EVERY SUCCESSFUL
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>>
    <div class="approach-container">
        <div class="approach-image">
            <img src="public/KitchenPage/kitchen4.png" alt="Modern kitchen remodel" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="approach-content">
            <h2>How We Approach Kitchen Remodeling</h2>
            <p>
                A well-designed kitchen can elevate your entire home—blending beauty, comfort, and functionality into one space. That's why we begin every project by understanding your goals, layout needs, and lifestyle.
            </p>
            <p>
                From space planning and cabinetry to lighting, flooring, and appliances, our expert kitchen team are tailored to how you live and cook. Every detail is thoughtfully handled by our experienced team.
            </p>
            <p>
                Whether you prefer modern, transitional, or timeless designs, our experts bring your vision to life with high-end finishes, expert craftsmanship, and a smooth remodeling process from start to finish.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="approach-list-section">
    <h3>What’s included in a full kitchen remodel?</h3>
    <div class="approach-list">
        <div class="approach-list-col">
            <div class="approach-item">
                <span class="approach-item-icon">✔️</span>
                <div class="approach-item-content">
                    <h4>CUSTOM CABINETS INSTALLATION</h4>
                    <p>Built-in storage tailored to your kitchen layout and style — maximizing space, functionality, and design appeal.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="approach-item">
                <span class="approach-item-icon">✔️</span>
                <div class="approach-item-content">
                    <h4>COUNTERTOP REPLACEMENT</h4>
                    <p>Precision installation of granite, quartz, butcher block, or laminate countertops for durability, beauty, and ease of use.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="approach-item">
                <span class="approach-item-icon">✔️</span>
                <div class="approach-item-content">
                    <h4>LIGHTING DESIGN &amp; INSTALLATION</h4>
                    <p>Add recessed lights, under-cabinet LEDs, pendants, and task lighting to brighten your space and enhance ambiance.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="approach-item">
                <span class="approach-item-icon">✔️</span>
                <div class="approach-item-content">
                    <h4>LAYOUT RECONFIGURATION / OPEN CONCEPT CONVERSION</h4>
                    <p>Knock down walls or redesign flow for a more open, spacious kitchen connected to the dining or living area.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="approach-item">
                <span class="approach-item-icon">✔️</span>
                <div class="approach-item-content">
                    <h4>BACKSPLASH INSTALLATION</h4>
                    <p>Protect your walls and add visual texture with stylish backsplashes — ceramic, glass, mosaic, or stone.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="approach-list-col">
            <div class="approach-item">
                <span class="approach-item-icon">✔️</span>
                <div class="approach-item-content">
                    <h4>PLUMBING &amp; SINK UPGRADES</h4>
                    <p>Install modern sinks, faucets, pot fillers, and relocate plumbing as needed to match the new design.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="approach-item">
                <span class="approach-item-icon">✔️</span>
                <div class="approach-item-content">
                    <h4>ELECTRICAL WORK &amp; APPLIANCE REWIRING</h4>
                    <p>Move or add outlets, switches, circuits, and connect built-in appliances like ovens, cooktops, or microwaves.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="approach-item">
                <span class="approach-item-icon">✔️</span>
                <div class="approach-item-content">
                    <h4>RANGE HOOD &amp; VENTILATION SYSTEMS</h4>
                    <p>Proper ventilation is key. Install or upgrade your range hood to remove smoke, odors, and excess heat.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="approach-item">
                <span class="approach-item-icon">✔️</span>
                <div class="approach-item-content">
                    <h4>FLOORING REPLACEMENT</h4>
                    <p>Install tile, luxury vinyl plank (LVP), hardwood, or waterproof laminate flooring for a long-lasting, clean look.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="approach-item">
                <span class="approach-item-icon">✔️</span>
                <div class="approach-item-content">
                    <h4>PAINTING &amp; FINAL FINISHES</h4>
                    <p>Complete the project with fresh wall paint, trim, and finishing touches to tie everything together.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>